Summary: Biochemical reaction from vortioxetine sulfoxide to vortioxetine sulfoxide glucuronide.
Biochemical reaction from vortioxetine to vortioxetine sulfoxide. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP3A4, CYP2A6, CYP2C8 or CYP3A5.

Controller: AOX1, CYP2C19, CYP2C9, CYP2D6, alcohol and aldehyde dehydrogenases
Summary: Biochemical reaction from vortioxetine to vortioxetine benzoic acid. This interaction can be catalyzed by alcohol and aldehyde dehydrogenases, AOX1, CYP2D6, CYP2C9 or CYP2C19.
Biochemical reaction from vortioxetine to 4-hydroxy-phenyl vortioxetine. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C9 or CYP2D6.
